  "lyrics": "better let's go la la la la la la la la la la la la la la la la la la la la la la with you in the quiet of the night when the stars illuminate the sky you held me close and whispered dreams can't take you so high through every storm that rains you were my guiding light your sacrifice is unseen yet they all shape my life in the pages of my story you pin chapters of grace your selfless acts of love time cannot erase with every step I take I beg your hand in mine your sacrifices will raise me up oh wings of love so true through every trial and every tear you saw me through your strength became my fortress your love my endless sea oh the sacrifices you've made they're always shaping me yeah in the tapestries of life your love's the golden thread stitching dreams into reality where love knows no end with every breath I take I feel your love's embrace your sacrifice will fuel my journey and every step I trace or take it's always your sacrifices you raise me up oh wings of love so true through every trial and every tear you saw me through your strength became my fortress your love my endless sea oh the sacrifices you've made they're forever shaping me so here's my vow to you my heart sings forever in every rise and every fall your love clings forever with gratitude and love walk the path you pave for the sacrifices you've made in your love in your love unsaved",
